    "sn24.39:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 24.39 ",
    "sn24.39:0.2": "2. Dutiyagamanavagga ",
    "sn24.39:0.3": "Rūpīcaarūpīcaattāsutta ",
    "sn24.39:1.1": "Sāvatthinidānaṁ. ",
    "sn24.39:1.2": "“Rūpī ca arūpī ca attā hoti arogo paraṁ maraṇā”ti …pe…. ",
    "sn24.39:1.3": "Ekavīsatimaṁ. "
  },
